    {
      "chinese": "[---]\r\n依居住地區劃分為五個亞群：（一）南勢阿美：花蓮市、新城鄉、吉安鄉、壽豐鄉。（二）秀姑巒阿美：鳳林鎮、光復鄉、瑞穗鄉、玉里鎮、富里鄉。（三）海岸阿美：豐濱鄉、長濱鄉、成功鎮以北。（四）馬蘭阿美：成功鎮以南、東河鄉、馬蘭平原一帶等。（五）恆春阿美：鹿野鄉、關山鎮、池上鄉、屏東縣滿州鄉一部份。",
      "ab": "Pakayni i kitiraan ko pafafida tona lima a kasa’etal Sakacecay, ka’amisay a ’Amis, Nafakowan, Singceng, Yosino, Rinahem. Sakatosa, Siwkolang a ’Amis, Cingalo’an, Fata’an, Kohkoh, Poseko, Kongpo. Sakatolo, Sawaliay a ’Amis, Fakong, Kakacawan, sa’amisan no Madawdaw. Sakasepat, Falangaw a ’Amis, satimolay no Madawdaw, Fafokod, o dafdaf no Falangaw. Sakalima, Palidaw a ’Amis, Palayapay, Tidatidan, Fanaw, Pingtong a Palidaw.",
      "order": "2",
      "sound": "https://dzywvpqnys6mw.cloudfront.net/files/2025/02/07/804f93534c85ad25c5e0f51889c3620a.mp3",
